                                    <TextBlock Foreground="#FF00B294" FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI" FontSize="38" Width="40" Height="18" TextAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center">゛゜</TextBlock>
